title: JAA ATPL Exam Preparation
description:
JAA ATPL Exam Preparation
	

Details 

Since the commencement of the JAA-ATPL examinations in January 2000, Oxford Aviation Training has entered over 1,500 students for more than 20,000 individual examination papers.

Our unrivalled experience in this area has led to our compiling a comprehensive bank of JAA-ATPL style questions from which we bring to you, on this disk, a selection of over 2,600 questions.
